## Limitations

The findings are based on available literature and may not capture all possible barriers to community involvement in research. The perspectives and experiences of specific communities may vary, and additional qualitative research could provide deeper insights. Furthermore, the sources used are limited to those accessible online and may not include the most recent developments in community-based research practices.